<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.8.10">
<l>ceṅka yaltiḷaik kuñcu ṉaittiru vēṅka</l>
<l>ṭattuṟai celvaṉai</l>
<l>maṅkai yarttalai vaṅka likaṉṟi vaṇṭa</l>
<l>miḻcceñcol mālaikaḷ</l>
<l>caṅkai yiṉṟi<supplied>t</supplied>ta rittu raikkaval lārkaḷ tañcama tākavē</l>
<l>vaṅka mākaṭal vaiyaṅ kāvala rāki vāṉula kāḷvarē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who are able to recite, remembering without hesitation,</l>
<l rend="indent">these garlands of fine words in elegant Tamil</l>
<l>[By] Kalikaṉṟi, chief of those of Maṅkai, about the beneficent one</l>
<l rend="indent">who dwells in Tiruvēṅkaṭam,</l>
<l>With pools where red carp play, since that [recitation] becomes an aid,</l>
<l>Becoming the guardians of the earth, with its the great, wavy sea,</l>
<l rend="indent">they will rule the heavenly world.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
